{"tid":625039,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"靠得住 真係米之蓮極品 ［多圖］","createTime":"2018-04-11T06:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T06:16:20.000Z","uid":139194,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"65bfdd89f525327ec65502f75be170f6ba8cf121","tid":625039,"uid":139194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:16:20.000Z","msg":"難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/140614_c61f2af658766c44ff9a3d9a8114426f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F140614_c61f2af658766c44ff9a3d9a8114426f.png&h=ff405abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先係服務差<br />\n第一次叫職員拎熱水，佢話等一陣，轉頭就冇咗回事。<br />\n第二次再叫直頭唔應你走咗入廚房。咁我就自己入水吧浸水。見到有個職員呢埋係角落頭玩手指。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當下已經感到有少少不滿。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其次係食物質素<br />\n深水埗牛腩麵好食過米之蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n份量小，牛腩撈麵只有三舊牛腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到咁嘅情況即刻再搵職員，咁佢就黑口黑面咁，<br />\n一首拎起我碗野走咗，最後我碗牛腩撈麵有六舊牛腩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n論食物分量、食物質素、員工服務、員工態度<br />\n都唔明白佢邊忽 米之蓮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  正評 垃圾靠唔住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評 米之蓮極品"}]}